प्रयागराज में जब कुम्भ लगता हैं तो सारा प्रयागराज ही कुम्भ हो जाता हैं। यहां के निवासी भी श्रद्धेय हो जाते है, प्रयागराज को एक खूबसूरत शहर के रूप में विकसित करने में और कुम्भ के सफल आयोजन करने में यहां के निवासियों ने भी पूरे देश को एक प्रेरणा दी है: पीएम #ModInKumbh

पिछली बार मैं जब यहां आया था तो मैंने कहा था कि इस बार का कुंभ अध्यात्म, आस्था और आधुनिकता की त्रिवेणी बनेगा। आज मुझे खुशी है कि आपने अपनी तपस्या से इसको साकार किया है। तपस्या को तकनीक से जोड़कर जो अद्भुत संगम बनाया गया, उसने भी सभी का ध्यान खींचा है; पीएम #ModiInKumbhpic.twitter.com/SVmH67XBBb

मैं पहले भी प्रयागराज आता रहा हूं, लेकिन गंगा जी की इतनी निर्मलता पहले नहीं देखी है। गंगाजी की ये निर्मलता नमामि-गंगे मिशन की दिशा व सरकार के सार्थक प्रयासों का उदाहरण है। इस अभियान के तहत प्रयागराज में गंगा में गिरने वाले 32 नाले बंद कराए गए हैं: पीएम #ModiInKumbh

पिछली बार मैं जब यहां आया था तो मैंने कहा था कि इस बार का कुंभ अध्यात्म, आस्था और आधुनिकता की त्रिवेणी बनेगा। मुझे खुशी है कि आप सभी ने अपनी तपस्या से इस विचार को साकार किया है। तपस्या के क्षेत्र को तकनीक से जोड़ कर जो अद्भुत संगम बनाया गया उसने भी सभी का ध्यान खींचा है: PM

Ordinary patriotic Indians who do not have the benefit of strategic inputs as would be available to Congress Party now, would also know the response on the above points.

I am sure there would be many serious inputs relating to the security strategy that experts would give to the Congress Party along with that to serve petty political gains, do not politicise defence procurement on false and imaginary facts. It hurts defence preparedness.

When our intelligence agencies conduct anti-insurgency operations along with the security forces (e.g. Ishrat Jahan case), do not let lose investigative agencies on the intelligence and security network of India.

When security personnel fight the terrorists and make sacrifices (e.g. Batla House), do not legitimise terrorism by standing shoulder to shoulder with the terrorists and call the war against terror as a fake encounter.
Politicians of any shade of opinion should not get into slanging match with any of the services personnel or their Chief. The Chief of a Force can’t be described as a ‘Sadak ka Goonda’.

Do not encourage indiscriminate illegal immigration into India & block steps which are taken to stop it. It hurts national security. Our Armed forces are amongst the most professional organisations & which have served this country exceedingly well.

Do not trivialise a serious national concern on terrorism as has been done by the Congress Spokespersons in the past two days. Next time if extremists & separatists raise slogans on how to break India (JNU incident), no one from mainstream parties should pay a supporting visit.
Do not give an impression to the world that India is divided on how to fight terrorism. When the world is rallying around India, the Opposition in India should not be striking a discordant note.

It is intriguing that the Party which has ruled the country for over half a century should need to be educated on national security concerns. I am sure amongst the various advices that experts will render to the Congress President on strategic issues, a few would be essential.

The appointment of General Hooda is significant. It is a belated & grudging recognition & acceptance of the surgical strikes of 2016 with which the General was intrinsically associated. I am sure he would educate the Party leaders that the surgical strikes were no routine step.

Congress President announced appointment of Lt. Gen. D.S. Hooda (Retd.), a distinguished fmr officer of Indian Army & a committee headed by him to advice the Party on National Security Policy. I have not the least doubt that he would give valuable advice to the grand old Party.

ऊर्जा गंगा परियोजना से बरौनी में फिर से शुरू किये जा रहे फर्टिलाइजर कारखाने को गैस उपलब्ध होगी। पटना में पाइप के माध्यम से गैस पहुंचाने का कार्य होगा, सीएनजी से गाड़ियां चल पाएंगी और हज़ारों परिवारों को अब पाइप वाली गैस मिलने लगेगी : पीएम मोदी

बिहार में स्वास्थ्य सेवाओं की दृष्टि से आज एक ऐतिहासिक दिन है। छपरा और पुर्णिया में अब नए मेडिकल कॉलेज बनने वाले हैं, वहीं भागलपुर और गया के मेडिकल कॉलेजों को अपग्रेड किया जा रहा है। इसके अलावा, बिहार में पटना एम्स के अलावा एक और एम्स बनाने पर काम चल रहा है: PM

एनडीए सरकार की योजनाओं का विजन, दो पटरियों पर है। पहली पटरी है इंफ्रास्ट्रक्चर से जुड़ी योजनाएं, औद्योगिक विकास, लोगों को आधुनिक सुविधाएं, दूसरी पटरी है उन वंचितों, शोषितों, पीड़ितों का जीवन आसान बनाना जो पिछले 70 वर्षों से मूलभूत सुविधाओं के लिए संघर्ष कर रहे हैं: PM

मैं पटना वासियों को बधाई देता हूं, क्योंकि पाटलिपुत्र अब मेट्रो रेल से जुड़ने वाला है। 13 हज़ार करोड़ रुपए की इस परियोजना को वर्तमान के साथ भविष्य को जरूरतों को ध्यान में रखते हुए विकसित किया जा रहा है। ये मेट्रो प्रोजेक्ट तेजी से विकसित हो रहे पटना शहर को नई रफ्तार देगा: PM

हमारी सरकार द्वारा कनेक्टिविटी पर भी विशेष बल दिया जा रहा है। आज यहां से रांची-पटना साप्ताहिक एक्सप्रेस को हरी झंडी दिखाई गई है। इसके अलावा बरौनी-कुमेदपुर, मुजफ्फरपुर-रक्सौल, फतुहा-इस्लामपुर, बिहारशरीफ-दनियावान, रेल लाइनों के बिजलीकरण का काम पूरा हो चुका है: PM
आज यहां हज़ारों करोड़ की परियोजनाओं का लोकार्पण और शिलान्यास किया गया है। इनमें पटना शहर को स्मार्ट बनाने और बिहार के औद्योगिक विकास एवं युवाओं को रोज़गार देने से जुड़ी योजनाएं शामिल हैं : पीएम मोदी
इस परियोजना का तीसरा लाभ ये होगा कि जब यहां पर उद्योगों को पर्याप्त मात्रा में गैस मिलेगी उससे Gas Based Economy का नया इकोसिस्टम विकसित होगा, युवाओं को रोज़गार के नए अवसर मिलेंगे: PM

इस परियोजना से 3 बड़े काम एक साथ होने जा रहे हैं। बरौनी में जो फर्टिलाइजर का कारखाना फिर से चालू किया जा रहा है, उसको गैस उपलब्ध होगी। पटना में पाइप के माध्यम से गैस देने का काम होगा, सीएनजी से गाड़ियां चल पाएंगी। हज़ारों परिवारों को अब पाइप वाली गैस मिलने वाली है: PM

इसी योजना के पहले चरण में जगदीशपुर-हल्दिया पाइपलाइन के पटना-फूलपुर सेक्शन का लोकार्पण किया गया है। जुलाई 2015 में मैंने इसकी आधारशिला रखी थी। हल्दिया–दुर्गापुर LPG पाइपलाइन का भी विस्तार मुजफ्फरपुर और पटना तक किया जा रहा है, जिसका शिलान्यास किया गया है: PM

यह एक ऐसा समय हैं जब हम सभी को एक साथ आना होगा और भारत को मजबूत और सुरक्षित बनाने के अपने संकल्प को और बल प्रदान करना होगा। मैं सभी राजनीतिक दलों से अपील करता हूं कि आइए हम राजनीति से ऊपर उठकर पूरी दुनिया को बतायें कि हम साथ हैं। हम सबके लिये वतन के आगे कुछ नहीं है।

130 करोड़ भारतीय, राष्ट्र की सेवा में अपना जीवन समर्पित करने वाले हमारे देश के वीर सैनिकों के परिवारों के साथ पूरी एकजुटता के साथ खड़े हैं। आने वाली पीढ़ियां उनकी वीरता को याद करेंगी। हम घायलों के शीघ्र से शीघ्र स्वस्थ होने की प्रार्थना करते हैं।

पुलवामा में हुए कायरतापूर्ण आतंकी हमले से पूरा देश गहरे शोक में है, इस तरह की घृणा और हिंसा को बढ़ावा देने वाली बर्बर मानसिकता के ख़िलाफ़ देश में आक्रोश हैं। प्रधानमंत्री श्री @narendramodi ने देश को आश्वस्त किया है कि हमारे शहीदों का बलिदान व्यर्थ नहीं जायेगा।

This report remains a Chowkidar Auditor General Report. 5/5 #RafaleCAGReport

The reason the numbers have not been declared is that dollar for dollar, the deal costs more than before. The report has hidden behind the Aligned Price. The lack of numbers makes comparison of costs meaningless. 4/5 #RafaleCAGReport

In fact, the CAG report noted this oversight on the Bank Guarantee when it says "However, Audit noted that this was actually a saving for M/s Dassault Aviation when compared to its previous offer of 2007." But failed to account for it in the main table. 3/5 #RafaleCAGReport

The bank guarantee which was present in the previous deal and would have constituted an additional 7% cost is not present in the new deal. So the so-called savings of 2.86% can be attributed to the cost of the missing bank guarantee. 2/5 #RafaleCAGReport

This is the first time in history that a CAG report to Parliament has redacted numbers. This in itself raises a big question mark on the report. The comparison of the prices is based on the Aligned Price, the calculation of which is opaque. 1/5 #RafaleCAGReport

Now without a shred of evidence, a fictional conflict of interest of the CAG is invented. How many more lies will be peddled to sustain a sinking dynast? India, certainly deserves better.

The use of an incomplete document is certainly not in consonance with the spirit of free speech. The ‘no integrity pact’ argument is belied by the fact that even in earlier purchases through inter-governmental agreement with Russia and the United States, such pacts were not there
The procedure argument that there was no Defence Acquisition Council, no CCS, no Contract Negotiation Committee was a blatant lie.
The dynast and his friends have in the past even attacked the Supreme Court when it rejected the writ petition on Rafale. The entire pricing argument was factually wrong.

I say this without fear of contradiction that no file or paper relating to the Rafale transaction ever reached him nor was he in any way, directly or indirectly, associated with the decision making on defence purchases.

In relation to the Rafale deal where thousands of crores of public money has been saved, a new falsehood is manufactured on a daily basis. The latest is in relation to the present CAG and his participation in the decision making process of Rafale.
How many lies are necessary to be peddled to save a sinking dynasty? The contagion effect of falsehood is fairly large. It appears to have spread to other colleagues in the ‘Mahajhootbandhan’.

The ‘slave’ mentality of senior leaders of Congress Party convinces them that they must only sing the song scripted by the dynast. A contrarian opinion will cost them their political career. When the dynast speaks lies, they all join the chorus.

In modern world dynasties inherently have their limitations. Aspirational societies abhor kingdoms. They insist on accountability and performance. But the grand old party of Indian politics has sadly become a captive of a dynasty.

In mature democracies those who deliberately rely on falsehood are banished from public life. With the changing socio-economic profile of India this will inevitably happen in India. Whatever be the number of peddled lies it can not to sustain a sinking dynasty.

2019 Election will be either Modi Vs. Chaos or Modi Vs. Anarchy. Mamata Banerjee’s latest acrobatics are the best evidence of the kind of governance India’s opposition can provide.

Curiously, the AICC President somersaulted his position from Saradha being a scam to “shoulder-to-shoulder”support to scamster. Interestingly, the first family of Congress where most members are on bail. A non-ideological short-lived coalition of opposition is disaster for India.

When Mamata Banerjee decided to sit on a Dharna she received support of many opposition parties who aspire to be in power. Most of them, or their affiliates are today being investigated, prosecuted and in some cases have also been convicted for crimes of corruption.

Today the CBI is being brutally prevented by physical force and detention of its officer from investigating a crime legally within its jurisdiction, in the State of West Bengal. It is a textbook illustration of a State Government assaulting Federalism.

It would be a gross error to assume that she did this because of a routine investigation involving a Police Officer. She did it to defocus from other opposition aspirants for the highest office and to project herself as the nucleus of India’s opposition.

Sh. Kharge is part of a Collegium that discharges a governance function. The position of Sh Kharge as the LOP in the Lok Sabha, entitles him to sit in the Committee but the political colour of that office has to be left outside, unfortunately, that does not seem to have happened.

The only thing constant in the High Powered Committee comprising of the Prime Minister, the Chief Justice of India and the Leader of the Opposition which deals with the CBI Director’s appointment and transfer, is the Kharge dissent.

Sh. Kharge’s dissent in the matter of the transfer of Alok Verma was coloured by his political views. He was a petitioner in the Supreme Court himself in support of Alok Verma. He should have recused himself from the Committee since his views were known

A dissenter challenges the majority. He does it on the basis of a call of conscience dictated by his fair mind. He puts his dissent on record so that it can be of value to the wisdom of the future generations. A dissent should never be a political tool.
Sh. Kharge dissents regularly. He dissented when Shri Alok Verma was appointed, dissented when Shri Alok Verma was transferred and has now dissented when Shri R. K. Shukla has been appointed.

Shri Kharge has dissented a bit too frequently. Many may wonder if Collegium’s are workable. The appointment of a CBI Director was never envisaged to be a political battle. Shri Kharge has made it look like one.
Has Mr. Kharge Brought Down the Value of Dissent? https://bit.ly/2HPen9t

Higher direct and indirect tax collections in 2016-17 and 2017-18 are an indicator of high growth in those two years. Growth is based on estimates, but tax collections are real.
If there is no job creation, as alleged, there should have logically been a great social unrest in the country. Past five years have passed off without a single major protest movement.
Last year the Government restored the benefit of Standard Deduction to salaried taxpayer at Rs.40,000/-. This year this benefit is being extended to Rs.50,000/-.
In a further calibrated move, those in the income bracket of Rs.3 to 5 lakhs witnessed their tax liability being halved from 10% to 5% and today this category has been completely exempted.

The tax exemption limit was first raised from Rs. 2 lakhs to Rs. 2.5 lakhs by the NDA Government. Thereafter, without altering the slabs, people earning upto Rs. 3 lakhs were exempted from payment of taxes.

In another step towards farmers' welfare, the Budget has announced today a significant income support scheme for every eligible land owning family involved in agriculture who will now be entitled to a sum of Rs. 6,000/- annually.

GST has already brought down most taxes on goods from 31% tax to the 18%, 12% and the 5% bracket. Never in the history of India during the five year tenure of a Government we have witnessed tax reduction and a Middle Class relief of this magnitude.
The future vision is to make India a Five Trillion Dollar economy. By the middle of the next decade we will achieve this and thereafter, target doubling that size of the economy.
The economic reforms undertaken by the NDA Government have unshackled Indian economy, unleashed its potential and made us a global leader in growth.

देश में घुमंतू समुदाय सदैव से उपेक्षित व विकास से वंचित रहा है। मोदी सरकार द्वारा इस वर्ग के कल्याण के लिए बनाये गए “कल्याण बोर्ड” और उनकी पहचान के लिए नीति आयोग अंतर्गत बनाये गए आयोग से उनके विकास के प्रयासों को स्थायित्व और गति देने के लिए मैं मोदी सरकार को धन्यवाद देता हूँ।

संगठित क्षेत्र में कार्यरत मजदूर और कामगारों को 7000 रुपए तक का बोनस और बोनस मिलने के लिए पात्रता को 21,000 प्रति माह बढ़ने के निर्णय से निचले स्तर पर कार्यरत वर्ग को बड़ी राहत देने के निर्णय का ह्रदय से स्वागत करता हूँ।

मोदी सरकार ने अपने पहले दिन से ही उत्तरपूर्व के विकास को प्राथमिकता दी है। इस बजट में उत्तर पूर्व के विकास के बजट को 21% बढ़ा कर 58 हजार करोड़ करने के लिए मैंप्रधानमंत्री मोदी जी को धन्यवाद देता हूँ। इस निर्णय से उत्तर पूर्व भी देश के विकास की मुख्यधारा से तेजी के साथ जुड़ेगा।

वर्षो से उपेक्षित देश की सुरक्षा सदैव मोदी सरकार की प्राथमिकता रही है। मोदी सरकार ने अपने हर निर्णय से हमारे सैनिकों का मनोबल और देश का मान बढ़ाया है। आज मोदी जी द्वारा रक्षा बजट को अब तक का सर्वाधिक 3 लाख करोड़ रुपए करने पर उनका ह्रदय से धन्यवाद देता हूँ।

किसान क्रेडिट में दिए जाने ब्याज में 2% कि छूट और समय से ऋण चुकाने पर 3% छूट से किसानो को 5% तक ब्याज में छूट देने का निर्णय किसानो को बड़ी राहत देगा। इस किसान हितेषी निर्णय के लिए मोदी जी का अभिनंदन।

1 लाख गांवों को डिजिटल करने के निर्णय से गाँव और शहर की दूरियां कम होंगी और ग्रामीण क्षेत्र भी देश के विकास में बराबर की सहभागिता निभा सकेंगे। अब गाँव भी न सिर्फ देश बल्कि वैश्विकस्तर के ज्ञान, विज्ञान और तकनीकी का लाभ ले सकेंगे।

महिलाओं का सशक्तिकरण मोदी सरकार की प्राथमिकता रही है। मोदी जी ने महिलाओं के विकास को महिलाओं के नेतृत्व में विकास में परिभाषित करके दिखाया है। प्रधानमंत्री मातृ वंदना योजना और माताओं को धुएं के अभिशाप से मुक्त करने वाली उज्ज्वला योजना के लक्ष्य को 8 करोड़ करना इसी का परिचायक है।

ఆవేదన ఉండదా మాకు? తమిళులకి ఎన్ని ఇచ్చారు? గుజరాత్‌కి ఎన్ని ఇచ్చారు..? వినేవాళ్లు ఉంటే ఎన్నైనా చెప్తారు. మహిళలు వచ్చి.. పోరాడతామంటున్నారు, వాళ్ల పెన్షన్ డబ్బులు విరాళంగా ఇచ్చి ఆంధ్ర ప్రజలకు పౌరుషం లేదా అని అడుగుతున్నారు. సాధారణ మహిళలకు ఉండే పరిజ్ఞానం కూడా మీకు లేదా?
బీజేపి నేతలు సిగ్గు లేకుండా మాట్లాడుతున్నారు. కేంద్ర సంస్థలు ఎవరి కోసం ఇస్తాయి, ఎవరి సొమ్ము ఇస్తున్నాయి? ప్రజాప్రతినిధిగా ఉండే అర్హత కూడా కోల్పోయారు. మీ మాటలు వింటుంటే రక్తం ఉడికిపోతుంది.

देश की जीडीपी में अमूल्य योगदान देने वाले मछुवारा समुदाय के कल्याण के लिए केंद्र सरकार में “मत्स्य पालन” विभाग बनाये जाने के लिए मैं प्रधानमंत्री श्री नरेंद्र मोदी जी के प्रति आभार व्यक्त करता हूँ। किसान क्रेडिट कार्ड का लाभ मछुवारा समुदाय को देने से उन्हें बहुत लाभ मिलेगा।

इस योजना में सरकार और लाभार्थी की सहभागिता से करीब 10 करोड़ गरीब श्रमिकों को 60 वर्ष की आयु के बाद Rs.3000 रुपए तक का मासिक पेंशन देने का निर्णय मोदी सरकार ने लिया है जिसके मैं उनका आभार व्यक्त करता हूँ।
प्रधानमंत्री ‘श्रम योगी मानधन योजना’, दशकों से विकास की मुख्यधारा से वंचित असंगठित क्षेत्र में कार्यरत देश के गरीब श्रमिकों के प्रति मोदी सरकार की संवेदनशीलता की परिचायक है।

गौ माता का सनातन संस्कृति व भारतवर्ष से अटूट रिश्ता है। मोदी सरकार द्वारा 750 करोड़ रुपए से इसके संरक्षण और संवर्धन के लिए ‘राष्ट्रिय कामधेनु आयोग’ एक अभूतपूर्व कदम है। मैं इस ऐतिहासिक निर्णय के लिए मोदी सरकार का कोटि-कोटि अभिनंदन करता हूँ।
यह फैसला किसान कि आय दो गुना करने के प्रयास में मील का पत्थर साबित होगी, इसके लिए मैं भाजपा के करोड़ों कार्यकर्ताओं की ओर से प्रधानमंत्री श्री @narendramodi जी का हृदय से अभिनंदन करता हूँ।

2 हेक्टेयर से कम भूमि वाले गरीब किसानों के लिए ‘प्रधानमंत्री किसान सम्मान योजना’ एक ऐतिहासिक पहल है। जिसके अंतर्गत देश के करीब 12 करोड़ किसानों को मोदी सरकार द्वारा 75000 करोड़ रुपए के बजट से प्रति वर्ष 6000 रुपए दिए जायेंगे।

आज के बजट ने यह पुनः प्रमाणित किया है कि मोदी सरकार देश के गरीब, किसान और युवाओं के सपने एवं आकाँक्षाओं को समर्पित सरकार है। इस सर्वग्राही बजट के लिए मैं प्रधानमंत्री श्री @narendramodi जी व उनकी पूरी सरकार को बधाई देता हूँ।

A special 8th book, which i loved more than all the others: Swimmer Among the Stars by @KanishkTharoor, a wonderful collection of stories that break conventions of time&space, evoking w/insight & compassion our old&new worlds. By a hugely talented writer who happens to be my son.

7/7 The One Hundred Year-Old Man Who Jumped out of a Window and Disappeared by Jonas Jonsson: The funniest, most joyous book I have read in years. Twentieth-century history retold through an ingenious plot in a comic caper that never ceases to surprise and delight. @OmarAbdullah
6/7 The Book of Laughter and Forgetting by Milan Kundera: A moving, evocative experience of East European history, informed by a rare insight into humanity. @ishaantharoor
5/7 The Saga of Khassak by OV Vijayan: This was originally a Malayalam novel that invented magic realism years before Gabriel García Márquez attempted it. @TharoorAssociates

4/7 Heavy Weather by P. G Wodehouse: One of the funniest of Wodehouse’s well-crafted masterpieces, among the many others he’s written; any one of several other masterworks by him would do as well. @TharoorBhakt
3/7 One Hundred Years Of Solitude by Gabriel García Márquez; extraordinary, magical reinvention of the Latin-American experience. @kanishktharoor
2/7 The Discovery of India by Jawaharlal Nehru; a profound vision of what has made India and Nehru. @SunilKhilnani
1/7 The Mahabharata: the great epic, embracing story, philosophy, psychology, politics and more. “What is here, is nowhere else”; the epic boasts; “what is not here, is nowhere”. @bibekdebroy

Projects worth over Rs. 182 crore were launched / inaugurated today in the states of Arunachal Pradesh, Nagaland and Assam. I am glad to share that, with this, projects worth more than Rs. 224 crore have been rolled out in NER within a span of just one week.

Understanding the potential of dual purpose of Tapioca plantation, Eri Silk Development for Sustainable Livelihood to Women through Tapioca was launched in Kokrajhar. It will benefit 1400 people & result in 45 MT of Eri Spun Silk, 200 MT of Eri Pupae & 5000 MT of Tapioca tuber.

Foundation stone was laid for Eri Spun Silk Mill in Bodoland Territorial Council. The mill will provide employment to nearly 1500 farmers through backward linkage and over 700 weavers through forward linkage.

Soil to Silk project aims to develop Eri-culture in Udalguri district through 100 acres of new Eri plantation & rejuvenation of existing 600 acres plantation. The project once completed will generate employment for over 7000 people annually.
Continuing the North East visit, launched several Sericulture projects for the state of Assam in Udalguri.pic.twitter.com/cat5Cxac3u

Following Hon PM vision of developing Aspirational Districts, project for Sericulture Development was launched for Aspirational dist. Kiphire of Nagaland. Project covering 600 acres of Eri & 100 acres of Mulberry plantation will produce 16 MT Eri Spun Silk & 1.43 MT Oak Tussar.

Project for Development of Bivoltine Sericulture launched in Wokha district of Nagaland is aimed at creating sustainable livelihood for women & encouraging pre-cocoon & post-yarn activities. Production of quality bivoltine silk will also help in reducing its import.

Post Cocoon Technology project was dedicated in two blocks of Mokokchung district - Chungtia & Sabangya. This project which encompasses skill training to 400 women will create post cocoon linkages from spinning, reeling, weaving to finished silk products with marketing support.

Established in Mokokchung, Muga P3 Basic Seed Production Centre covering over 1000 farmers will produce and supply basic Muga seed to other units thereby helping the state of Nagaland play a vital role in fulfilling requirement of Muga dfls in NER.
Many would be surprised to know Chungtia in Nagaland produces some of the best South India Silk sarees - a shining example of ‘Ek Bharat, Shreshtha Bharat’.pic.twitter.com/VQv5rCiOGL
